<li id="cite_note-15"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-15">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">For a discussion of the slight changes that affect the mean solar day, see the <a href="/wiki/%CE%94T_(timekeeping)" title="ΔT (timekeeping)">ΔT</a> article.</span>
