<li id="cite_note-16"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-16">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><cite id="CITEREFRicci" class="citation web cs1">Ricci, Pierpaolo. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.pierpaoloricci.it/dati/giornosolarevero_eng.htm">"The duration of the true solar day"</a>. <i>pierpaoloricci.it</i>. <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20090826184737/http://www.pierpaoloricci.it/dati/giornosolarevero_eng.htm">Archived</a> from the original on August 26, 2009.</cite><span title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.jtitle=pierpaoloricci.it&amp;rft.atitle=The+duration+of+the+true+solar+day&amp;rft.aulast=Ricci&amp;rft.aufirst=Pierpaolo&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pierpaoloricci.it%2Fdati%2Fgiornosolarevero_eng.htm&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3ASolar+time" class="Z3988"></span></span>
